OL,5, Indigenous leaders met Prince Charles  
OL,6, in Canada and asked for an apology from
OL,7, the Queen over the "assimilation and   
OL,8, genocide" of indigenous schoolchildren.
OL,10,FRoseAnne Archibald, Assembly of First  
OL,11,FNations national chief, said the prince
OL,12,F"acknowledged" failures in handling the
OL,13,Frelationship with indigenous people.   
OL,15,FCanada is dealing with a scandal which 
OL,16,Fsaw indigenous children die or be      
OL,17,Fabused in residential schools.         
OL,19,FThere have been calls for the Queen to 
OL,20,Fapologise over the issue.              
